rows.label: tev022901_MSG0001
rows.name:
Neither Sakuraba nor Grenada GG make any Skell
equipment that really speaks to me, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev022901_MSG0002
rows.name:
But now there's that new Meredith & Co. joint that
opened after we landed here on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev022901_MSG0003
rows.name:
Their stuff is way cooler than anything coming out
of stodgy old Sakuraba or Grenada. I really dig it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev022901_MSG0004
rows.name:
I've managed to save up a nice chunk of change
after doing business with Shiraton.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev022901_MSG0005
rows.name:
I've been thinking of making a new Gold Courage Skell
tricked out entirely in Meredith & Co. parts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev022901_MSG0010
rows.name:
I'm just getting one person after another asking me to
dispose of their dangerous waste.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev022901_MSG0011
rows.name:
To put it in Zaruboggan terms, folks just bring us
voltant and piles of money.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev022901_MSG0012
rows.name:
Then I give the junk to Shiraton and he cleans it up.
I'm making money hand over fist![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev022901_MSG0013
rows.name:
Heh heh heh. And it's all thanks to you turning a blind
eye to that little kerfuffle with me and Shiraton.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev022901_MSG0014
rows.name:
One of these days, we gotta rent out a restaurant and
have a little drinking party to celebrate the bright future
of humans and Zaruboggan![ST:wait ]
